167 (i) The department of public health shall create a written informational resource in
168 English and Spanish summarizing the requirements of this statue.
169 (j) All chain restaurants shall report annually to the department of public health whether
170 they offer children’s meals and if so, that they understand their obligations under this section.
171 Such reporting must be done on a form prescribed by the department and must be signed by a
